\n[[File:220913 Jesuit Church in Piotrk\u00f3w Trybunalski - 02.jpg|thumb|[[Piotrk\u00f3w Trybunalski]]]]\n[[File:Pomnik Jana D\u0142ugosza w Pabianicach.jpg|alt=|thumb|[[Pabianice]]]]\n[[File:Kutno, Ratusz, mur., 1 po\u0142. XIX (bakel2006).jpg|thumb|[[Tomasz\u00f3w Mazowiecki]]]]\n[[File:Wola Chojnata - pa\u0142ac-003.JPG|thumb|Palace in [[Wola-Chojnata]]]]\n\n\u0141\u00f3d\u017a Voivodeship is divided into 24 counties ([[powiat]]s): 3 city counties and 21 land counties. These are further divided into 177 [[gmina]]s.\n\nThe counties are listed in the following table (ordering within categories is by decreasing population).<ref name=\"LDB\" />\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n! English and<br> Polish names\n! Area<br> {{small|(km\u00b2)}}\n! Population<br> {{small|(31 December 2018)}}\n! Seat\n! width=\"30%\" align=\"center\"|Other towns\n! Total<br> [[gmina]]s\n|-bgcolor=\"F0F8FF\"\n|colspan=6|'''City counties'''\n|-\n| [[\u0141\u00f3d\u017a]]\n| align=\"right\"|293\n| align=\"right\"|685,285 {{decrease}}\n| colspan=2 |\n| align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| [[Piotrk\u00f3w Trybunalski]]\n| align=\"right\"|\n| align=\"right\"|73,670 {{decrease}}\n| colspan=2 |\n| align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n| [[Skierniewice]]\n| align=\"right\"|33\n| align=\"right\"|48,178 {{decrease}}\n| colspan=2 |\n| align=\"center\"|1\n|-bgcolor=\"F0F8FF\"\n|colspan=6|'''Land counties'''\n|-\n|[[Zgierz County]]<br> powiat zgierski\n| align=\"right\"| 854\n| align=\"right\"|165,916 {{increase}}\n|[[Zgierz]]\n|[[Ozork\u00f3w]], [[Aleksandr\u00f3w \u0141\u00f3dzki]], [[G\u0142owno]], [[Stryk\u00f3w]]\n| align=\"center\"|9\n|-\n|[[Pabianice County]]<br> powiat pabianicki\n| align=\"right\"| 491\n| align=\"right\"|119,289 {{decrease}}\n|[[Pabianice]]\n|[[Konstantyn\u00f3w \u0141\u00f3dzki]]\n| align=\"center\"|7\n|-\n|[[Sieradz County]]<br> powiat sieradzki\n| align=\"right\"| 1,491\n| align=\"right\"|118,240 {{decrease}}\n|[[Sieradz]]\n|[[Z\u0142oczew]], [[Warta, Poland|Warta]], [[B\u0142a